Running Instructions:

Run the "run.bat" file

!IMPORTANT!
* If the MongoDB server directory in your computer is different than: "C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.4\bin\mongod.exe" - You should replace it in the "run.bat" file
* In order to change the screen id (The default value is 3), open 'js/main.js' file and change line 4 to the wanted value (var screenId = 3;)